<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="start-v">start <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /stɑːt/    美 /stɑːrt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-begin">1.★ <strong>开始(begin)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The show <strong>started with</strong> a piece of music familiar to people in their fifties.
演出以一段五十多岁的人耳熟能详的经典音乐开始。</p><footer>2013 上海</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>start to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Henry Ford did not start to build his first car until 1896.
直到1896年，亨利·福特才开始制造他的第一辆轿车。</p><footer>2011 辽宁</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>start doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The locals knew nothing about me, but slowly, they started teaching me the art of being a neighbour.
当地人对我一无所知，但慢慢地，他们开始教我做邻居之道。</p><footer>2013 江苏</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-set-out">2.★ <strong>出发；启程(set out)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>start for Beijing
动身去北京</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>发动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He couldn’t start the car.
他无法发动汽车。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The engine won’t start.
引擎发动不起来。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>创办；开办：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>start a newspaper / company
创办报纸/公司</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to start my own business.
我想开办自己的公司。</p><footer>2011 陕西</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="get-started">get started</h3>
<p>1.<strong>开始；着手；动手：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s nearly ten o’clock. Let’s get started.
都快10点了，我们开始吧。</p></div>

<h3 id="start-off-out">start off / out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>出发；启程；起先：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ll have to start out / off early to get there by lunchtime.
我们得早点出发，以便在午饭前赶到那里。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I started off as a conductor but became a bus driver.
我起初是售票员，但后来成了公共汽车司机。</p></div>

<h3 id="start-up">start up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>创立；组建：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>start up businesses
创办企业</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>启动；发动：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The driver got back the car and started up.
司机回到车上发动了引擎。</p></div>

<h3 id="to-start-with">to start with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>首先；起初：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was pretty nervous to start with, but after a while I was fine.
起初我相当紧张，但过了一会儿就好了。</p></div></div>